[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0448","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0448.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0264","title":"Miva htmlscript 2.x 目录遍历漏洞","description":"Miva htmlscript 2.x 中的 CGI 程序存在目录遍历漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过特制的 URL 路径参数，绕过路径限制访问服务器上的任意文件（如密码文件、配置文件等）。该漏洞影响 htmlscript 2.x 版本，攻击者只需发送 HTTP 请求即可利用，危害等级中等，建议升级至最新版本或禁用该 CGI 程序。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0264"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1998-01-27T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:01.847","remediation":"升级 Miva htmlscript 至 3.0 或更高版本，该版本已修复目录遍历问题；如产品已停止维护，应立即从 Web 服务器 cgi-bin 目录中移除 htmlscript CGI 程序。临时缓解措施：在 Apache/Nginx 层面配置规则拦截包含 \"../\" 的 URL 请求，或通过 .htaccess 限制对 htmlscript 脚本的访问来源。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0264","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20434","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/0cda26301f5b3e56ace35e3d98835812d878db41/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0264.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0264","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0264.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/638fc08494602a9faf37bf81043122f16d26625c/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0264.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-h676-3v8p-5vwf/GHSA-h676-3v8p-5vwf.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/snort/drop-rules/sid-msg.map","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0264.json","https://github.com/slacker247/GPDA/blob/fa9006d0877a691f1ddffe88799c844a3e8a669a/Sodi/Run/IDSrules/rule.829","https://github.com/jdkoftinoff/mb-linux-msli/blob/8adb103e34af9ff1d8d122e9ee2a1808836f0a14/uClinux-dist/user/snort/drop-rules/web-cgi.rules","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--2d13d37d-5c85-422a-bd4e-7e51f93842cc.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0448.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0447","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0447.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0263","title":"Oracle Solaris SUNWadmap 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"Sun Solaris 操作系统中的 SUNWadmap 管理工具包（admintool）存在本地权限提升漏洞。admintool 程序以 setuid root 权限运行，本地普通用户可利用该程序在参数处理上的缺陷，以 root 权限执行任意命令，从而获取系统完全控制权限。该漏洞影响 Solaris 2.5、2.5.1、2.6 等多个版本，攻击者需拥有本地账户，攻击复杂度低，无需认证即可利用。Sun 已发布安全公告（SunSolve Bulletin #173）提供修补方案。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0263"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1998-07-16T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:01.717","remediation":"建议立即移除 /usr/sbin/adm/admap 二进制文件的 setuid 权限：`chmod u-s /usr/sbin/adm/admap`；如无需使用 Solstice AdminSuite，可直接卸载 SUNWadmap 软件包：`pkgrm SUNWadmap`；同时安装 Sun 对应补丁（如 106235-xx 系列补丁，视 Solaris 版本而定）；限制 admap 仅授权管理员可执行，防止普通用户滥用提权。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://sunsolve.sun.com/pub-cgi/retrieve.pl?doctype=coll&doc=secbull/173"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0447.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0446","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0446.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0262","title":"Hylafax 4.0 pl2 Faxsurvey CGI 远程命令执行漏洞","description":"Hylafax 4.0 pl2 的 faxsurvey CGI 脚本未对用户输入进行有效过滤，远程攻击者可通过在查询字符串中注入 shell 元字符（如分号、管道符等）实现任意命令执行。该漏洞影响 Linux 平台上的 Hylafax 4.0 pl2 版本，攻击者无需身份认证，只需向目标服务器发送特制的 HTTP 请求即可触发，可能导致服务器完全受控。CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0262"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1998-08-04T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:01.590","remediation":"升级到 Hylafax 4.1 或更高版本，移除或禁用 faxsurvey CGI 脚本，限制 CGI 目录的执行权限，在 Web 服务器层面过滤传入 query string 中的 shell 元字符（如 `;`、`|`、`$`）。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/2056","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1532","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20462","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/0cda26301f5b3e56ace35e3d98835812d878db41/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0262.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0262","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0262.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/638fc08494602a9faf37bf81043122f16d26625c/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0262.json","https://github.com/swimlane/soc-faker/blob/361c4ae88956878fbd8aaf5975044328556dfecd/socfaker/data/alert_names.txt","https://github.com/decal/werdlists/blob/81edb463f7f6311c85defefaf75ac9cd58e5cfb9/exploit-info/symantec-attack-signatures.txt","https://github.com/NetBSD/pkgsrc-wip/blob/6723edd43ced2a9627d0c0e8bf12d208cfde84d5/sara/PLIST","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/snort/drop-rules/sid-msg.map","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0262.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0446.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0445","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0445.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0260","title":"多款Web服务器 jj CGI程序 远程命令执行漏洞","description":"jj CGI 程序存在命令注入漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向该 CGI 程序传递包含 shell 元字符（如分号、管道符等）的特制请求参数，在目标服务器上以 Web 服务器进程权限执行任意系统命令。该漏洞影响早期运行 jj CGI 程序的 Unix/Linux 系统，攻击者无需身份认证即可远程利用，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。建议禁用或移除受影响的 jj CGI 脚本。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0260"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1996-12-24T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:01.353","remediation":"立即删除 jj CGI 脚本（通常位于 /cgi-bin/jj 路径），该脚本已过时且不适用于现代 Web 服务环境。如因兼容性必须使用，请在 Web 服务器配置中限制 CGI 执行权限并启用输入过滤，但最安全的做法是完全移除该 CGI 程序。同时审查服务器上其他 CGI 脚本是否存在类似 shell 元字符注入问题。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0260","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/297eb115816d3735806f02ee33bb4d2d53ecd5c6/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0260.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0260","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0260.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0260.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2ed73314b4d66512efbb22e0644e615bc00001f2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0260.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-vqmv-6xp5-qh75/GHSA-vqmv-6xp5-qh75.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/snort/drop-rules/web-cgi.rules","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/J/jj.nasl","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/slacker247/GPDA/blob/fa9006d0877a691f1ddffe88799c844a3e8a669a/Sodi/Run/IDSrules/rule.1183"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0445.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0444","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0444.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0259","title":"cfingerd 用户信息泄露漏洞","description":"cfingerd 是一款可配置的 finger 服务守护程序，由于其未对用户查询进行充分的访问控制过滤，远程攻击者可通过向目标系统发送特制的 `search.**@target` 查询请求，枚举系统上所有已注册用户账号信息，造成敏感信息泄露。该漏洞影响使用 cfingerd 的 Unix/Linux 系统，攻击者可在未授权条件下远程利用，为进一步的社会工程学攻击或密码爆破提供用户列表基础。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0259"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-05-23T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:01.240","remediation":"升级 cfingerd 至 1.4.3 或更高版本以修复用户列表泄露漏洞；如无法升级，建议在 inetd/xinetd 配置中禁用 finger 服务（注释掉 finger 行），或使用 tcpwrappers（hosts.allow/hosts.deny）限制可访问源 IP。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0259","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0259.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/297eb115816d3735806f02ee33bb4d2d53ecd5c6/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0259.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0259","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0259.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2ed73314b4d66512efbb22e0644e615bc00001f2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0259.json","https://github.com/eldondev/Snort/blob/34bdcf6a7a638b55c7c04f77ef1efa526ad08e33/doc/signatures/322.txt","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/snort/drop-rules/finger.rules","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-m4g2-9rpr-wc96/GHSA-m4g2-9rpr-wc96.json","https://github.com/jdkoftinoff/mb-linux-msli/blob/8adb103e34af9ff1d8d122e9ee2a1808836f0a14/uClinux-dist/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/cfinger_search.nasl","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0444.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0443","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0443.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0258","title":"Microsoft Windows 95/NT 4.0 IP Fragmentation 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Microsoft Windows 95 和 Windows NT 4.0 的 IP 碎片重组模块存在缺陷，远程攻击者可通过发送特制的畸形 IP 分片数据包（Bonk 变种），利用 UDP 协议的分片偏移量计算错误，导致目标系统内核崩溃或蓝屏死机，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞无需认证即可远程触发，影响 Windows 95 及 Windows NT 4.0 所有版本。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0258"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-02-13T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:01.117","remediation":"升级至 Windows 2000 或更高版本系统，已不受此漏洞影响。若因特殊原因仍运行 Windows 95/NT 4.0，安装 Microsoft 1999 年安全更新 MS99-017（KB191725）可修复 IP 分段重组校验逻辑。临时缓解措施：在路由器/防火墙上阻断进入内网的畸形 IP 分片包，或限制入站 ICMP 流量降低攻击面。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=88901842000424&w=2","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/5917e2b15694e167c1fd9ad85775b2bdfc5fe29c/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0258.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0258","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0258.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0258.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a55bddfc5dd568e972e08b703ab596ed3580b7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0258.json","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/B/bonk.nasl","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0258.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154000_154100.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/e7bd3e92452a8dc8da42d94ae3ba208936d5a5b9/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0443.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0442","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0442.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0257","title":"Linux Kernel IP Fragmentation Nestea 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"CVE-1999-0257 即 Nestea 变种 Teardrop IP 碎片拒绝服务攻击，攻击者向目标系统发送精心构造的、偏移量重叠的畸形 IP 分片数据包，目标系统在重组这些分片时因算法缺陷导致内存计算错误，引发系统崩溃或重启。该漏洞无需认证即可远程利用，影响 Linux Kernel 2.6.20.1 及众多早期操作系统版本，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0257"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-04-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:00.990","remediation":"升级 Linux 内核至 2.6.20.1 以上版本（如 2.6.21+），该漏洞已在后续版本中修复。无法升级时，可在 iptables 中添加规则丢弃畸形 IP 分片包：iptables -A INPUT -f -m limit --limit 100/s --limit-burst 100 -j ACCEPT 或使用防火墙过滤分片重叠的恶意数据包作为临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0257","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/5917e2b15694e167c1fd9ad85775b2bdfc5fe29c/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0257.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0257","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0257.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0257.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a55bddfc5dd568e972e08b703ab596ed3580b7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0257.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-5h5w-wrfr-qmhc/GHSA-5