itle":"L-Soft LISTSERV 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"tags. Let me craft a good Chinese description.<value>LISTSERV 邮件列表管理软件存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，由于程序在处理用户输入（如特定命令参数）时未对数据长度进行充分边界校验，导致超长输入可覆盖内存相邻区域。远程攻击者无需身份认证，只需向 LISTSERV 服务发送特制构造的恶意命令请求，即可触发缓冲区溢出并覆盖返回地址，进而实现任意命令执行。该漏洞影响早期版本 LISTSERV（如 1.8a 等），攻击者可借此完全控制运行该服务的服务器，执行任意系统命令、读取或篡改数据，危害程度较高。修复方式为升级至已修复的 LISTSERV 版本并限制服务网络访问。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0252"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:00.383","remediation":"立即升级 LISTSERV 至 1.8c 或更高版本，该版本已修复缓冲区溢出漏洞。无法立即升级时，在防火墙限制对 LISTSERV 端口（如 25/SMTP）的访问，仅允许受信 IP 连接，并监控异常请求以降低风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0252","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0252.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab6ab436962e16237b21ed9d4458dafc38c692fc/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0252.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0252","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0252.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a55bddfc5dd568e972e08b703ab596ed3580b7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0252.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0252.md","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0252.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--c6cefb8e-0a81-40ca-8e3d-51d21f448702.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/Ethishh/securin_assessment/blob/e6ce9197b6593ae46f3f5646d268181eea6cbb31/cve_sync.log"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0437.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0436","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0436.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0251","title":"Unix Talkd 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Talkd（talk守护进程）存在拒绝服务漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可向目标系统发送特制请求，破坏目标用户的终端显示内容，导致正常会话中断或系统服务异常。该漏洞影响早期Unix/Linux系统中运行的talk服务，攻击者可通过网络连接利用该缺陷进行远程拒绝服务攻击。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0251"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:00.253","remediation":"立即禁用 talkd 服务（`systemctl disable talkd --now` 或 `killall talkd`），并在防火墙层面拦截 UDP/TCP 517 端口（`iptables -A INPUT -p udp --dport 517 -j DROP`）。如业务需要使用 talk 服务，应升级操作系统的 talkd 实现至修复版本或迁移至加密替代方案。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0251","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0251.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab6ab436962e16237b21ed9d4458dafc38c692fc/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0251.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0251","https://github.com/edoardottt/missing-cve-nuclei-templates/blob/36c16d53eb6071e39cfc3cf88e99f1b340ec913b/data/year/1999.txt","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0251.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a55bddfc5dd568e972e08b703ab596ed3580b7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0251.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-4pmp-8rgh-2hrv/GHSA-4pmp-8rgh-2hrv.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0251.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x83000/82087/info.html","https://github.com/CVEDB/Poc-Git/blob/0275aeb329b0747c9a1d46160c921eae06095557/1999/CVE-1999-0251.md"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0436.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0435","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0435.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0250","title":"Dan Bernstein Qmail SMTP 命令处理拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Qmail 1.01 的 SMTP 组件在处理超长命令时存在拒绝服务漏洞。远程攻击者无需认证即可向目标服务器的 25 端口发送特制长 SMTP 命令，导致 qmail-smtpd 进程崩溃或异常终止，从而中断邮件服务。该漏洞影响 Dan Bernstein Qmail 1.01 版本，攻击复杂度低，且无需任何权限，可被用于阻断正常邮件收发功能。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0250"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-07-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:00.120","remediation":"立即升级至 Qmail 1.03 或更高版本，或在编译时添加 qmail-smtpd.c 中对输入行长度（LINE_MAX）的显式检查。如不便升级，可在 SMTP 服务前端部署流量过滤规则，限制单行 SMTP 命令长度不超过 512 字节。长期建议迁移至 Netqmail 补丁集（netqmail 1.06）以获得持续维护。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://cr.yp.to/qmail/venema.html","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=87602558319024&w=2","http://www.ornl.gov/its/archives/mailing-lists/qmail/1997/06/threads.html","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0250.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab6ab436962e16237b21ed9d4458dafc38c692fc/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0250.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0250","https://github.com/edoardottt/missing-cve-nuclei-templates/blob/36c16d53eb6071e39cfc3cf88e99f1b340ec913b/data/year/1999.txt","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0250.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a55bddfc5dd568e972e08b703ab596ed3580b7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0250.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-wq5m-pq24-j5cv/GHSA-wq5m-pq24-j5cv.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x83000/82079/info.html","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0250.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0435.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0434","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0434.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0249","title":"Microsoft Windows NT RSHSVC 远程代码执行漏洞","description":"Windows NT 与 Windows 2000 系统中的 RSHSVC（远程 Shell 服务）存在远程代码执行漏洞。未经身份认证的远程攻击者可利用该服务缺乏足够访问控制的问题，通过网络连接向目标系统的 RSHSVC 端口发送特制请求，从而以系统权限执行任意命令，实现完全控制目标主机。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 4.0 及 Windows 2000 版本，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0249"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:59.987","remediation":"Windows NT 4.0 和 Windows 2000 均已生命周期结束，建议立即升级到受支持版本的 Windows（如 Windows Server 2019/2022）以彻底消除该漏洞。如无法升级，可采取缓解措施：通过服务管理器停止 RSHSVC 服务并将启动类型设为\"禁用\"；同时在防火墙层面阻止外部对 TCP 514 等 rsh 相关端口的访问，限制仅授权管理 IP 可访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0249","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0249.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab6ab436962e16237b21ed9d4458dafc38c692fc/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0249.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0249","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0249.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a55bddfc5dd568e972e08b703ab596ed3580b7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0249.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0249.md","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0249.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154200_154300.json","https://github.com/Ethishh/securin_assessment/blob/e6ce9197b6593ae46f3f5646d268181eea6cbb31/cve_sync.log"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0434.toml"}]